# Musik KITA Operations System (musik-kita-ops)

Sistem administrasi & keuangan internal studio musik **Musik KITA**. Menggantikan proses Excel.
Solo developer pemula — **pilih approach paling mudah dipahami**, jelaskan alasannya.

**Source of truth lengkap:** `CLAUDE.md` v1.6 (Jun 2026). Update rules ini jika CLAUDE.md berubah.

## Tech Stack

- Laravel 11, PHP 8.3, MySQL (Laragon), Blade + Tailwind 3 + Alpine.js (Breeze — **JANGAN Bootstrap**)
- Vite, Spatie Permission v6 (RBAC), LAN lokal offline (Fase 1)
- Path: `C:/laragon/www/musik-kita-ops`

## Roles

| Role | Akses |
|------|-------|
| **Owner** | Full access, ubah harga, hapus master, manage user, void payment, audit log, tandai honor/gaji staff dibayar, CRUD karyawan & slip gaji staff |
| **Admin** | Operasional harian — TIDAK boleh ubah harga, hapus master, manage user, void payment |
| **Auditor** | Read-only |
| **Guru** | Portal `/guru/*` — jadwal, absensi sesi sendiri, honor read-only, laporan progres (lihat `docs/srs/modules/M10-guru-portal.md`) |

Route sensitif (harga, honor payroll, staff-payrolls write, invoice-component) → `role:Owner`. Operasional → `role:Owner|Admin`. Read → `role:Owner|Admin|Auditor`.

## Konvensi Kode

- Komentar: **Bahasa Indonesia** | Variabel/method: English | UI & validasi: **Bahasa Indonesia**
- Validasi di **Form Request**, bukan Controller
- Spatie Permission + audit log untuk action penting
- Controllers di root `App\Http\Controllers\` (TIDAK subfolder Admin/)
- Business logic kompleks → `App\Services\`

## Larangan Kritis

- Instruksi ambigu → **TANYA dulu**, jangan asumsikan
- Jangan hapus/pindah file tanpa konfirmasi
- Jangan `migrate:fresh` tanpa konfirmasi eksplisit (hapus semua data!)
- Jangan push `.env` ke Git
- Schema: `packages.code` (bukan name), `duration_min`, `price_per_month`, `students.full_name`, `student_code`
- `class_type`: `REGULER|HOBBY|DUO|KIDS_CLASS|KIDS_CLASS_BUNDLE` (KAPITAL)
- Status murid: Title Case (`Calon`, `Trial`, `Aktif`, `Cuti`, `Selesai`, `Mengundurkan Diri`)
- Kolom `students.package_id`, `assigned_teacher_id`, `assigned_room_id`, `preferred_day/time` **SUDAH DIHAPUS** — pakai `$student->primaryEnrollment`
- Metode bayar: `CASH|TRANSFER|QRIS|DEBIT`
- Invoice wajib punya `enrollment_id`
- Trial = 30 menit semua tipe | Trial no-show honor = Rp 0
- Honor cut-off H-2 sebelum akhir bulan | Transport honor = input manual
- Void payment & hapus diskon → Owner saja
- Kids Class usia 4 s/d <5 tahun
- Bootstrap ❌ | TypeScript `any` ❌

## Checklist Sebelum Generate Code

- [ ] Kolom & enum benar (lihat rule database)
- [ ] Tailwind CSS, bukan Bootstrap
- [ ] Role check Spatie + audit log
- [ ] Relasi murid via enrollment / primaryEnrollment
- [ ] Diskon: parent_item_id + discount_reason wajib
- [ ] Komentar ID, pesan UI ID
- [ ] Gaji staff: slip `GAJI/YYYY/MM/NNNN` (bukan `SLIP/` honor guru)
- [ ] Guru tidak masuk `employees` — honor via M06
- [ ] Mark/void paid gaji staff → Owner; expense kategori `GAJI_STAFF`

## Git Commit Format

```
[Modul/Area] Deskripsi singkat
```
Contoh: `M02: Tambah form Trial Class dengan validasi`

## Data Operasional

~300 murid, **18 guru** (confirmed), ~1.200 sesi/bulan, 18 slip honor/bulan.
